We thank the reviewer for the in-depth and insightful comments. Here is our response to the comments:

\section*{1. Gaps in the Literature}
\begin{itemize}
    \item We have stated the literature gaps on page 2.
    \item  see ``Potential Contributions'' on page 2, where we introducd the effectiveness of TRW in detecting anomalies, and suggested the importance of temporal patterns in identifying irregularities..
